.za 1.5
.ue 1
                                                                      $..#$
                                           <Calw Sonntg>* 5 </6>* August 83
                                                 <erh. 20 August Montg 83>*
Dear Children [Hermann]

.ue 2
                                                                      $..#$
Forts.: 5 </6>* August 83
Since new years I have not sent you a line and even now it is but a word of
love; for though mine eyes are some what better I am to spare them a great
deal; so reading and working is to be put aside for ever I suppose; however
the Lord is good and helps me to say Amen to His will and learn many things
I would not have known without this trail

Many thanks for your letters, by your last ones we are much rejoiced to
hear that your health is quite restored, dear Mama and children will also
have thanked God for His goodness towards you; may He give you grace to use
it to His praise and for the salvation of many.

Much love to my dear Tine to the dear children
.
                        With a kiss Yours affectly
.fo -
                                            J. Gundert


